01:04:35,960 --> 01:04:37,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika bukan karena dia,</font>

1104
01:04:37,889 --> 01:04:40,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hu tidak akan hilang selama ini.</font>

1105
01:04:40,829 --> 01:04:43,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga. Kamu serius?</font>

1106
01:04:44,230 --> 01:04:46,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Itu benar.</font>

1107
01:04:47,740 --> 01:04:50,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mendengar dan melihatnya.</font>

1108
01:04:52,069 --> 01:04:53,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

1109
01:04:54,480 --> 01:04:55,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu bilang kamu melihatnya.</font>

1110
01:04:56,379 --> 01:04:58,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa baru mengatakannya sekarang?</font>

1111
01:04:58,950 --> 01:05:01,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hu sudah tiada.</font>

1112
01:05:01,650 --> 01:05:04,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa gunanya mengatakannya sekarang?</font>

1113
01:05:06,049 --> 01:05:07,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

1114
01:05:08,359 --> 01:05:09,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Se Hu</font>

1115
01:05:10,619 --> 01:05:11,930
<font color=#FFFF00>masih hidup.</font>

1116
01:05:55,970 --> 01:05:57,809
<font color=#FFFF00>"Mengerang"</font>

1117
01:05:57,809 --> 01:05:58,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan.</font>

1118
01:05:58,809 --> 01:06:00,369
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hentikan. - Yang benar saja.</font>

1119
01:06:00,369 --> 01:06:01,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

1120
01:06:01,379 --> 01:06:03,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia hanya menurut jika kita memukulnya.</font>

1121
01:06:03,139 --> 01:06:04,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti sekarang.</font>

1122
01:06:04,410 --> 01:06:05,410
<font color=#FFFF00>"Pimpinan Goo serius berakting"</font>

1123
01:06:05,410 --> 01:06:06,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan.</font>

1124
01:06:07,619 --> 01:06:08,819
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang menyuruhmu?</font>

1125
01:06:10,990 --> 01:06:13,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Se Joon masih hidup, bawa dia kemari.</font>

1126
01:06:13,420 --> 01:06:16,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa dia kemari dan tanya apakah aku orangnya.</font>

1127
01:06:16,920 --> 01:06:18,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika itu Se Joon. Bukan, Se Hu.</font>

1128
01:06:19,230 --> 01:06:21,660
<font color=#FFFF00>"Aku Se Joon, Ibu"</font>

1129
01:06:21,960 --> 01:06:23,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini lelucon?</font>

1130
01:06:23,329 --> 01:06:25,430
<font color=#FFFF00>"Ibunya tidak mengenalinya"</font>

